Notes: Heather Bowman becomes Gonzaga's all-time leading scorer today. Bowman has now
scored 2,018 to surpass Tammy Tibbles mark of 2,011 scored from 1984-88.
Bowman also is the only player in WCC history to score 2,000-plus points.
